handleError: error reference: aReference	"Print a header before failing on an errro / syntax notification from the the script loaded by the given request"		"spit out a warning if in headless mode, otherwise a debugger will popup"	Smalltalk isHeadless 		ifTrue: [ self inform: 'Errors in script loaded from ', aReference fullName ].																															(error isKindOf: SyntaxErrorNotification)		"for syntax errors we can used the default action"		ifTrue: [ error defaultAction ]		"otherwise resignal it"		ifFalse: [ error pass ]